<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُبْصِرُونَ}</span> ... تَعْلَمُونَ قُبْحَهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَطَهَّرُونَ}</span> ... يَتَنَزَّهُونَ عَنْ إِتْيَانِ الذُّكْرَانِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
